title: The black-life protestors are chanting for "dead cops now" in Baton Rouge.
subtitle: A tape of black-life protesters shouting "Dead Police" until December 2014 has nothing to do with the events of the BLM protest of July 2016.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: The protestors in Baton Rouge were shouting "dead police now" shortly before three officers were killed in that city.
